skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: resistor analyzer
des: Ever found a resistor you've wanted to identify, or too busy to go look up that color chart? This skill lets you quickly and easily learn the resistance of resistors with 3-6 color bands on them, and also provides tolerance and temperature coefficient data (on 4-6 color band resistors). Even helps correct the common mistake of reading resistors backwards on common resistor values.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
